title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan and Special Guest Hillary
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan and Special Guest Hillary
description:
Morgan and Hillary catch up on life and share some recent love updates. They also talk about their celebrity sightings in Nashville, wild collections they had growing up and walk down memory lane with books!
